    'Before activating the webservice, you must be sure to: ' => 'Prije aktivacije web servisa, morate: ',
    'Check that URL rewriting is available on this server.' => 'Provjerite da li je URL rewriting omogućen na ovom serveru.',
    'Check that the five methods GET, POST, PUT, DELETE and HEAD are supported by this server.' => 'Provjerite da je pet je metoda GET, POST, PUT, DELETE i HEAD podržano na ovom serveru.',
