    'Use our [1]favicon generator on PrestaShop Marketplace[/1] to boost your brand image!' => 'Koristite [1] favicon generator na PrestaShop Marketplace [/1] kako biste poboljšali svoju sliku robne marke!',
    'Will appear on your main page. Recommended size for the default theme: height %height% and width %width%.' => 'Pojaviti će se na glavnoj stranici. Preporučena veličina za zadane teme: visina %height%, a širina %width%.',
    'It is the small icon that appears in browser tabs, next to the title.' => 'To je mala ikona koja se pojavljuje na karticama preglednika pored naslova.',
    'Be careful! Please check your theme in an RTL language before generating the RTL stylesheet: your theme could be already adapted to RTL.
